<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>ERP & CRM — F1 IT Solutions</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web@2.1.1/src/regular/style.css">
<style>
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html,body{margin:0;padding:0;}
  .ph{line-height:1;display:inline-block;}
  a{color:#2563FF;}
  a:hover{color:#1b54e6;}
  @keyframes cp-fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px);}to{opacity:1;transform:none;}}
  .cp-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #E6ECF7;border-radius:18px;padding:24px;transition:.2s;animation:cp-fade .35s ease both;text-decoration:none;display:block;color:inherit;}
  .cp-card.demo{cursor:pointer;}
  .cp-card.demo:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(20,40,110,0.12);transform:translateY(-2px);}
</style>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">
</head>
<body>
<div style="min-height:100vh;width:100%;font-family:'Inter',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;color:#0B1437;background:#FFFFFF;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;">

  <header style="position:sticky;top:0;z-index:400;padding:16px 24px 0;"><div id="gonj-nav"></div></header>

  <section style="max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:56px 24px 20px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.6px;color:#7A5CFF;background:rgba(122,92,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(122,92,255,0.22);padding:7px 14px;border-radius:30px;margin-bottom:22px;">ERP &amp; CRM</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,46px);line-height:1.1;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;margin:0 0 18px;">Software, die Ihre Abläufe bündelt</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.65;color:#45506E;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;">ERP- und CRM-Systeme, individuell für Ihr Unternehmen eingerichtet — für Kunden, Lager, Mitarbeitende und Projekte an einem Ort.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 24px 64px;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;">
      <a class="cp-card demo" href="PflegePilot.html"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#E6ECFB;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-squares-four" style="font-size:22px;color:#2563FF;"></i></div><span style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF,#7A5CFF);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;">Beispiel ansehen</span></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">ERP System</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Alle Geschäftsprozesse an einem Ort.</p></a>
      <a class="cp-card demo" href="DialPilot.html"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#F0ECFE;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-phone-outgoing" style="font-size:22px;color:#7A5CFF;"></i></div><span style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF,#7A5CFF);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;">Beispiel ansehen</span></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">CRM System</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Jede Kundenbeziehung im Blick.</p></a>
      <a class="cp-card demo" href="DialPilot.html"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#E2F6FE;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-address-book" style="font-size:22px;color:#21D4FD;"></i></div><span style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF,#7A5CFF);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;">Beispiel ansehen</span></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">Kundenverwaltung</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Kontakte, Angebote & Verträge zentral.</p></a>
      <a class="cp-card demo" href="PflegePilot.html"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#E6ECFB;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-package" style="font-size:22px;color:#2563FF;"></i></div><span style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF,#7A5CFF);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;">Beispiel ansehen</span></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">Lagerverwaltung</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Bestände in Echtzeit steuern.</p></a>
      <a class="cp-card demo" href="PflegePilot.html"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#F0ECFE;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-users-three" style="font-size:22px;color:#7A5CFF;"></i></div><span style="font-size:10.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF,#7A5CFF);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:7px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;">Beispiel ansehen</span></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">Mitarbeiterverwaltung</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Teams, Zeiten & Rollen verwalten.</p></a>
      <div class="cp-card"><div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;background:#E2F6FE;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><i class="ph ph-kanban" style="font-size:22px;color:#21D4FD;"></i></div></div><div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;">Projektmanagement</div><p style="font-size:14px;color:#45506E;line-height:1.55;margin:0;">Aufgaben, Budgets & Deadlines im Griff.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 80px;">
    <div style="background:linear-gradient(120deg,#2563FF 0%,#7A5CFF 55%,#21D4FD 100%);border-radius:22px;padding:48px;text-align:center;color:#fff;">
      <h2 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin:0 0 12px;">Brauchen Sie ein ERP- oder CRM-System?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:15.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 24px;line-height:1.6;">Wir beraten Sie unverbindlich zu Ihrem Bedarf.</p>
      <a href="index.html#kontakt" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;background:#fff;color:#0B1437;text-decoration:none;border-radius:11px;padding:14px 26px;font-weight:700;font-size:14.5px;"><i class="ph ph-envelope-simple" style="font-size:17px;"></i> Jetzt anfragen</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div id="gonj-footer"></div>
</div>
<script src="gonj-shared.js"></script>
<script>renderGonjNav('gonj-nav');renderGonjFooter('gonj-footer');</script>
</body>
</html>
